        <updateDate>2019-08-21T15:37:28Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill amends the federal bankruptcy code to increase the aggregate debt limit for a family farmer who files for relief under chapter 12 (family farmer or fisherman reorganization). The debt limit is the maximum amount of debt that can be reorganized in bankruptcy.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
